dct_title_s: Plan of Port-Lyautey and of Mehdia. G.S.G.S. 4241
dct_description_sm: United States. Army Map Service. Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. G.S.G.S. no. 4241. Alternate title: Port Lyautey. Two maps on one sheet. In upper left margin: Morocco 1:10,000. Relief shown by 2.5 meter contour intervals and spot elevations. Lambert conical orthomorphic projection. N.W.Africa zone grid. Inset: Port-Lyatney (1:50,000) taken from 1:50,00 sheet of Port-Lyautey (Kenitra). Copied from a french map dated 1935.
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1942.
